title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 42] New Wave, Post-Punk
description:
Here's four great records from the 80's, music that takes me back to a very happy time and place. Of course not as good as or even close to today's "meuzik" of great entertainers such as Miley Cyres, johans brothers, Rihanna and so on. May God have mercy on us! 

Part 42 brings you the music of:


Armoury Show - Waiting for the Floods [1985]

I Can Crawl - Desert (1986)

Sad Lovers and Giants - Feeding the Flame [1983]

Venus in Furs - Platonic Love & Other Stories [1984]


By the way I test-downloaded many of my torrents the other day and wanted to thank all of you who are still seeding those older torrents. Let this music be heard and re-discovered, though quarter a century late. Much appreciated!
